    <h3>3.5 Eksport EDI++ (Insert GT)</h3>

    <p><strong>Request:</strong></p>
    <pre><code>POST /api/v1/export/insert-gt/
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOi...
Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "company_id": 10,
  "date_from": "2026-03-01",
  "date_to": "2026-03-31",
  "include_private": false
&#125;</code></pre>

    <p><strong>Response <code>202 Accepted</code>:</strong></p>
